column5: Water temp 45deg and level dropped 2 ft from last weekend. Went 1 for 2. I fished hard for this little guy. 1000 drift fish.LOL
With that green grass it’s hard to tell what time year it is.   	wtg
That grass has been under water for the past 4-6 weeks. That how high the water has been. GBay must be dropping fast.
